{"tid":1876703,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★瘋搶！殯儀店推防疫套裝　紙紮口罩探熱器酒精乜都齊","createTime":"2020-02-12T14:29:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T05:36:14.000Z","uid":19454,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"ba7789f886360e2cd0dca9f0397241db17f576e1","tid":1876703,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T14:29:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3989611/org/c01265c246311284699b0d76d9de9dfc.jpg/lEiRVx9Gb_mPtUe8uutOJqHNkM-tDkEWEV_77hFf--4?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3989611%2Forg%2Fc01265c246311284699b0d76d9de9dfc.jpg%2FlEiRVx9Gb_mPtUe8uutOJqHNkM-tDkEWEV_77hFf--4%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=9c6da5a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3989683/org/bcf78f2f3e81a7f862f469d2186a6e43.png/dErisS8_Qgc7rR4KO7NyXQHemvbe_0zihlc7CYZXOwk?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3989683%2Forg%2Fbcf78f2f3e81a7f862f469d2186a6e43.png%2FdErisS8_Qgc7rR4KO7NyXQHemvbe_0zihlc7CYZXOwk%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=5ea509dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n台灣有殯儀用品店「希望傳承 骨罐.紙紮.生命寶石」在facebook貼出全套的抗疫紙紮祭品，當中包括一盒口罩，紙紮探熱槍和紙紮酒精，這些紙紮祭品做得十分緻細，例如紙紮口罩淺藍色的盒上還有一個醫護人員圖案，幾可亂真，裏面更有「口罩」，絕非只有空盒。<br />\n<br />\n店家指這是為客人特製的紙紮作品「天堂防疫組」，又指「就是掛念祢，無論祢在哪裡，即使祢到了天堂，家人一樣很想祢，很關心祢哦！我們一起防疫大作戰！」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/433272/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%8F%B0%E6%AE%AF%E5%84%80%E5%BA%97%E6%8E%A8%E5%A4%A9%E5%A0%82%E9%98%B2%E7%96%AB%E5%A5%97%E8%A3%9D-%E7%B4%99%E7%B4%AE%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E6%8E%A2%E7%86%B1%E5%99%A8%E9%85%92%E7%B2%BE%E4%B9%9C%E9%83%BD%E9%BD%8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E9%25A1%258C%2F433272%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%258F%25B0%25E6%25AE%25AF%25E5%2584%2580%25E5%25BA%259